cs.SY, cs.MA, cs.DC, cs.LG, cs.RO 

The paper deals with distributed event-triggered consensus in multi-agent systems, which involves control theory, optimization, and robotics. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.SY (Systems and Control), followed by cs.MA (Multi-Agent Systems) and cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing). The paper also uses optimization techniques, which could place it in cs.LG (Machine Learning) or cs.RO (Robotics).
